info.author: Mark Bonicillo
classifiers: License :: OSI Approved :: Apache Software License
info.name: volttron-platform-driver
info.summary: The Platform Driver agent is a special purpose agent that manages communication between the Volttron platform and devices. The Platform driver features a number of endpoints for collecting data and sending control signals using the message bus and automatically publishes data to the bus on a specified interval.
